\begin_inset Formula \[
\oint_{(C)}\frac{f(z)}{z-z_{0}}\,\tdc z=\int_{(C_{1})}\frac{f(z)}{z-z_{0}}\,\tdc z+\int_{(C_{2})}\frac{f(z)}{z-z_{0}}\,\tdc z\]

